(1068, 58, 'page_content', '<h4 class=\"text-h4\">Take advantage of this SPECIAL offer!</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-h4\">Until the coronavirus pandemic has been reduced or eliminated, LWE Inc. has reduced the price of The Rainbow Race app! Coming Soon!</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-h4\">The Rainbow Race (course) created because of Covid-19 is sold separate from the app and contains the storybooks, their discussion pages, and its “Certificate of Completion.” It is aimed toward children between the ages of 2–7 years old. The author, Stella Gain, has authentically signed the certificate. This certificate also has words of affirmation on it, and can be a reminder to stay positive no matter what, which is its message. This is a great way enrich a young child’s growth while ordered to “stay at home”. In the course, the storybooks are tangible with a child being able to turn the pages alongside an adult. This makes quality time a deeper bonding experience that can be invaluable toward a young child’s successful development. The Rainbow Race course is sold in our <span class=\"text-change\"><a href=\"##\">on-line store.</a></span></h4>\r\n<h5 class=\"text-h4\">If you know of children who are in a difficult situation, i.e. children in group homes or shelters, etc., please send us an email to <span class=\"text-change\"><a href=\"###\">Contact@TheRainbowRace.com</a></span> with their info and we will send them The Rainbow Race app for FREE! Please give us your info including email as well in case we have any questions.</h5>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-h4\">The Rainbow Race app makes a great gift for any little child you know! While we are all still primarily stuck at home, this is the perfect time for parents to work with their young kids to do something beneficial to help shape their future.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-h4\">Covid-19 inspired LWE to also produce The Rainbow Race into a tangible course a child can take with a parent at home. It comprises of the 7 books and discussion pages. These 2 activities are the main features of this product that enlighten children with positive awareness. This can also be a fun Christmas gift to spend quality time with a child. It has the same concept as The Rainbow Race App except it will also contain a “Certificate of Completion” personally and authentically signed by the author Stella Gain. The first 1000 copies of this course will be available at our on-line store. Keep checking.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-h4\">LWE Inc. agrees with child experts that if children under 7 years old were made to feel “noticed” and “valuable” at this precious time in their young lives, our future world would be a safer and more loving place to live. Please see <span class=\"text-change\"><a href=\"###\">“Endorsements.”</a></span></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-h4\">For the price of a fast food meal for two or even two lattes, an adult can spend hours of quality time with their young child while helping them to experience the entertaining, but constructive Rainbow Race; a race that can help guide young lives down the best road in order to be rewarded with good health and success!</h4>\r\n<h5 class=\"text-h4\">In the mean time, hunger impacts one out of every nine people on earth, and one in four of the world’s children are stunted due to malnutrition. That’s just plain unacceptable! We must all find a way to help these innocent children.</h5>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-h4\">LWE Inc. hopes to be a force of the future along with “Feeding the Children.” It IS possible and it starts with us.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-h4\">Enjoy this race because on the other side of the rainbow there is a possible golden existence for everyone!</h4>'),
