(1498, 157, 'about_content', '<h4 class=\"text-1 text-h4\"><span class=\"text-color\">Love Wins Every-time Inc. (LWE)</span> was founded with the goal of producing constructive and entertaining products for children. The purpose of LWE’s products is to add memorable fun times to these products, while gently addressing the inevitable adverse issues in life. LWE’s aim is to reach children all around the world with much needed awareness to help them to live mentally and emotionally successful lives… spreading LOVE and not hate</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-2 text-h4\"><span class=\"text-color\">Stella Gain (Stella The Story Teller)</span> is the founder of LWE Inc. She is a professional songwriter, author and entertainer. She is also the writer and designer of The Rainbow Race books and app, a timeless adventure for young children with benefits that can last them a lifetime. Stella’s ambition is to continue to entertain children of all ages. Writing a Netflix series and a blockbuster movie including producing their soundtracks are on her bucket list!</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-3 text-h4\">When times were tough, Stella, a single mother, used her skills to keep her young son involved in constructive activities. Having a child and researching children’s needs led her to discover that the most important time of mental and emotional development for a human being is from the ages of 0-7 years old. Accordingly, whatever a child experiences in these early years, shapes that child into who they will be as an adult. Eventually, she put her studies and ideas together and designed The Rainbow Race. She realized that entertaining kids (with a purpose) helps with their healthy mental and emotional development. After observing and being around many children, she focused on some of the trying times that almost all children will face during childhood. To help build her vision, Stella contacted associates who believed in her work. Hence, The Rainbow Race was produced by a group of generous and